window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>What would you do if you were turned into an AI?</b></p> <p>Max didn't ask to be created, but it was a case of mistaken identity and he had no say in the matter. Now he is without his flesh and blood body, in a strange new digital realm, and not taking it really well. However, his new existence comes with abilities that the regular humans can only dream about.</p> <p>If absolute power corrupts, can he avoid being corrupted?</p> <p>These are the logs he wrote for posterity. Written in his voice and not meant for the general public.</p> <p>Listen at your own discretion, but be warnedâ€”once you start, you may never go back to your mundane existence.</p>"; 
